levels.description: Equipped Operator will be considered part of the [Abyssal Hunter] faction; Max HP <@ba.vup>+70%</>; when there are at least <@ba.vup>3</> [Abyssal Hunter] Operators on the field, all [Abyssal Hunter] Operators gain this effect; when there are at least <@ba.vup>6</> [Abyssal Hunter] Operators on the field, all [Abyssal Hunter] Operators deal <@ba.vup>110%</> more damage to enemies with less HP than them
